author: Google
description:
Meet the Google #Pixel10 Pro Fold

🛡️ Design & Durability
- Two new colors
- A more durable design with a new gearless hinge
- IP68 dust and water resistance (a first for a foldable)

📖 Displays & Multitasking
- A larger outer display with smaller bezels
- An 8-inch Super Actua Flex inner display with up to 3000 nits of peak brightness
- Split Screen with window size control
- Drag and Drop for moving files between apps

⚡️ Performance & Battery
- The all-new Tensor G5 chip
- The biggest battery on a foldable device yet
- Pixelsnap built-in (a first for a foldable)

🤖 Cameras & AI
- A new 48MP wide camera
- Instant View for seeing photos alongside the viewfinder
- AI features like Camera Coach and Magic Cue
- One year of Google AI Pro included
title: Unboxing the new Pixel 10 Pro Fold
